Description: Interactive 3D visualization of large Cayley graphs using
    Vulkan-based rendering based on 'Datoviz' library.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: grDevices, stats
Suggests: cayleyR, knitr, rmarkdown, testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: C17, GNU make, pkg-config, Vulkan (>= 1.2) SDK
        (libvulkan-dev + glslc on Linux), GLFW3 (libglfw3-dev on
        Linux). Optional configure flag --with-simd enables SSE4.1 +
        PCLMUL for faster PNG screenshots (fpng); disabled by default
        for portability.
